#### Transaction 3: Dispute Resolution (Lines 3478-3555)
```javascript
await db.transaction(async (tx) => {
  if (award_to === 'creator') {
    // Full amount to creator (minus 15% fee)
    await tx.insert(agreementEarnings)...
  } else if (award_to === 'brand') {
